name: I Stell Noted Draw #6
description:
My New NFT Collection: "My ART Skill - Immortal"
was formed by aggravating 5 years of work history and persistent drawing with mild neck pain. 
This is a story about an artist who couldn't stop at the right moment, until the universe decided it for him, and now that she told me - enough! I want to capture this as art at the end. I still need to draw, but she has other plans for now, but for now I am gaining patience.
